#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:143
msgid ""
"The Diazo rules file is an :term:`XML` document containing rules to specify "
"where the content elements (title, footer, main text, etc.) will be located in "
"the targeted theme page. The rules are created using *rule directives* which "
"have *attributes*; attribute values are either CSS expressions or :term:`XPath` "
"expressions."
msgstr ""
"El archivo de reglas de Diazo es un documento :term:`XML` que contiene reglas "
"para especificar dónde se ubicarán los elementos de contenido (título, pie de "
"página, texto principal, etc.) en la página del tema de destino. Las reglas se "
"crean utilizando *directivas de reglas* que tienen *atributos*; Los valores de "
"atributo son expresiones CSS o expresiones :term:`XPath`."

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:148
msgid "CSS Selector Based Attributes"
msgstr "Atributos basados en selector CSS"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:149
msgid ""
"It is generally recommended that you use CSS3 selectors to target elements in "
"your content or theme. The CSS3 selectors used by Diazo directives are listed "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Por lo general, se recomienda utilizar selectores CSS3 para orientar los "
"elementos del contenido o tema. Los selectores CSS3 utilizados por las "
"directivas Diazo se enumeran a continuación:"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:152
msgid "``css:theme``"
msgstr "``css:theme``"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:153
msgid "Used to select target elements from the theme using CSS3 selectors."
msgstr ""
"Se utiliza para seleccionar elementos de destino del tema mediante selectores "
"CSS3."

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:154
msgid "``css:content``"
msgstr "``css:content``"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:155
msgid "Used to specify the element that should be taken from the content."
msgstr "Se utiliza para especificar el elemento que se debe tomar del contenido."

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:156
msgid "``css:theme-children``"
msgstr "``css:theme-children``"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:157
msgid "Used to select the children of matching elements."
msgstr ""
"Se utiliza para seleccionar los elementos secundarios de los elementos "
"coincidentes."

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:160
msgid "``css:content-children``"
msgstr "``css:content-children``"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:159
msgid "Used to identify the children of an element that will be used."
msgstr ""
"Se utiliza para identificar los elementos secundarios de un elemento que se va "
"a utilizar."

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:163
msgid "XPath Selector Based Attributes"
msgstr "Atributos basados en el selector XPath"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:165
msgid ""
"Depending on complexity of the required selector it is sometimes necessary or "
"more convenient to use :term:`XPath` selectors instead of CSS selectors. XPath "
"selectors use the unprefixed attributes ``theme`` and ``content``."
msgstr ""
"Dependiendo de la complejidad del selector requerido, a veces es necesario o "
"más conveniente usar selectores :term:`XPath` en lugar de selectores CSS. Los "
"selectores XPath utilizan los atributos sin prefijo ``theme`` y ``content``."

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:168
msgid "The common XPath selector attributes include:"
msgstr "Los atributos comunes del selector XPath incluyen:"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:170
msgid "``theme``"
msgstr "``theme``"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:171
msgid "Used to select target elements from the theme using XPath selectors."
msgstr ""
"Se utiliza para seleccionar elementos de destino del tema mediante selectores "
"XPath."

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:172
msgid "``content``"
msgstr "``content``"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:173
