msgstr ""
"Se utiliza para seleccionar los elementos secundarios de los elementos "
"coincidentes mediante selectores XPath."

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:177
msgid "``content-children``"
msgstr "``content-children``"

#: ../theming/ttw-advanced-2.rst:177
msgid ""
"Used to identify the children of an element that will be used using XPath "
"selectors."
msgstr ""
"Se utiliza para identificar los elementos secundarios de un elemento que se "
"usará mediante selectores XPath."

